					<h1 itemprop="name">Donald Trump’s Troubles Are Just Beginning</h1>

					<h3>By <span itemscope itemprop="author" itemtype="http://schema.org/Person"><meta itemprop="url" content="http://www.newyorker.com/contributors/john-cassidy" ><a href="http://www.newyorker.com/contributors/john-cassidy" title="John Cassidy" rel="author" itemprop="url"><span itemprop="name">John Cassidy</span></a></span></h3>					<div class="color-footer social-hover">
					
